window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Time is running out on John’s second chance</b><br> <br> John and his beautiful companions in the Heaven’s Shield Guild have returned from their overseas voyage victorious. But home isn’t like they left it–dungeons have started to disappear, corrupted by some unknown force.<br> <br> Unknown to everyone but John, that is. Invaders from a dying world are coming. And if they succeed, it marks the beginning of the end for John’s world.<br> <br> To survive the ultimate challenge, the Heaven’s Shied Guild must build their power as fast as they can. Can they win their race against time … this time? Or will it all come down to the choices of The Last Necromancer?<br> <br> <i>The Last Necromancer</i> is a LitRPG fantasy trilogy that contains game-like action, progressive stats, adventuring guilds, and slow burn harems. It’s perfect for fans of Atlas Kane and David Burke.</p>"; 
